com.samsung.android.service.health.tracking

Interface HealthTracker.TrackerEventListener

  • Enclosing class:
    HealthTracker

    public static interface HealthTracker.TrackerEventListener
    TrackerEventListener receives a sensor data event callback.
    Implement this interface to receive the event.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    HealthTracker.setEventListener(HealthTracker.HealthTrackerEventListener)
